Other records
: Swakop (
Marseul 1872
); Damaraland (
Kaszab 1956
); Namib Sand Sea desert (
Seely 2012
); 

Namibia

(
Bologna 2000a
; 

Pitzalis 
et al.
2014

).

Species greatly isolated in a possible monotypic group. It is well characterized by 11 antennomeres, dense silver setation on the body, but on elytra, mesosternum completely and densely setate, and unique elytral pattern (see 
Péringuey 1909
).
